Package: mospiR
Type: Package
Title: Client for the MoSPI Microdata portal
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Saket", "Choudhary", email = "saketkc@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download microdata from the MoSPI (Ministry of Statistics and
    Programme Implementation, Government of India) Microdata Portal
    <https://microdata.gov.in>. Provides functions to list datasets, list
    files within a dataset, and download individual files or entire datasets
    using the MoSPI NADA API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    pkgdown,
    nesstarR
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
